    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\t\tThings Can Only Get Better - Howard Jones\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nTabbed By : GubGub1234\r\ne-mail: gubgub1234@yahoo.com\r\n\r\nTuning: EADG\r\n\r\nIntro (Played lightly)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--0------------------------------------------0---------|\r\nA|----------------3--------------------------------------|\r\nE|-----------------------------0-------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nFirst Verse (Slapped)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----7-7-------------------------------|\r\nA|----------2--3----3-3/5---5h7----------|\r\nE|--5----------------------------3-3-4-4-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----7-7--------------------------------------------7-----------|\r\nA|----------2--3----3-3/5---5h7-----------------------------------|\r\nE|--5----------------------------3--4--5-------------------3--4--5|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------2--3-------------7-------------|\r\nE|--5--5-5-------------------------3-3-4-4-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------2---------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------2--3-------------7-------------|\r\nE|--5--5-5-------------------------3-3-4-4-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------2--3-----------5h7-------------|\r\nE|--5-x5-5-------------------------3-3-4-4-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------2--3---------------------------|\r\nE|--5--5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nLeading To Chorus\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--5-----------5-3----------3-7---------7-5---------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------0-0----------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--5-----------5-3----------3-7---------7-5---------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------0--0-0-------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus (Slapped)\r\nx4\r\nG|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------7-7----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------2--3---3--5-----5h7-------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--5-x---------------------------0-0-3--0-3/4------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse (Slapped)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------7-7----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------2--3---3--5-----5h7-------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--5-x---------------------------3-3-4-4-----------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------5h7----------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------7-7----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------2--3---3--5-------7-------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--5-x---------------------------3-3-4-4-----------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nAfter This Comes The \"Leading To Chorus\" Part\r\nThen Chorus\r\nThen Leading To Chorus Again\r\nThen The Solo (Just Play The Chorus Twice)\r\nThen Chorus four times until the song fades out\r\n\r\nThere may be a couple of cool little licks or fills i didn't tab, but they aren't too \r\nWhat i've written can go through the whole song.\r\n\r\n\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| \\  slide down\r\n| h  hammer-on\r\n| p  pull-off\r\n| ~  vibrato\r\n| +  harmonic\r\n| x  Mute note\r\n===============================================================================",
